short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analyzes and exposes potential spam links for Gmail.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Safe Gmail Links" is a Chrome extension designed to enhance email security. It exposes potentially harmful links within Gmail messages, offering users protection against phishing and malware attacks. With its robust detection capabilities, users can confidently navigate their inbox, knowing that their online safety is prioritized.

As this extension works within your browser, and not through an external server, no information sent anywhere.  Your private emails remain confidential, with only the links revealed for your review.

We collect nothing.  Your safety online and privacy is what matters most.

Need help?  Please reach out to safelinks@readadjust.com
